#: ../../user_manual/fitsviewer.rst:3
msgid "Chapter 6. FITS Viewer"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../user_manual/fitsviewer.rst:6
msgid ""
"FITS, or Flexible Image Transport System, is the standard format for "
"representing images and data in Astronomy. The KStars FITS Viewer is a tool "
"to view those images. It is not designed for editing of FITS Images."
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../user_manual/fitsviewer.rst:11
msgid ""
"The FITS Viewer can be automatically invoked for images received from the "
"camera. It can also be invoked directly from the main KStars menu. To open a "
"FITS file, select the ``File`` → ``Open Image...`` menu item, or press "
"**Ctrl**\\ +\\ **O**."
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../user_manual/fitsviewer.rst:16
msgid "|FITS Viewer|"
msgstr ""

